text: Choptank may refer to a location in the eastern United States or a former Native American tribe: *Choptank people ;Communities *Choptank, Maryland, Caroline County *Choptank Mills, Delaware, Kent County ;Other * Choptank (Middletown, Delaware), listed on the National Register of Historic Places listings in southern New Castle County, Delaware *Choptank Electric Cooperative, a not-for-profit energy organization *Choptank River, a tributary of Chesapeake Bay *Choptank River Fishing Pier, on the Choptank River *Choptank River Light, a lighthouse near Oxford, Maryland
title: Choptank
